snippet: “Jimmy P.” unconventionally tells the story of a troubled American Indian and war veteran and the psychoanalyst who tries to unlock the secrets of his personality.
abstract: A O Scott reviews Arnaud Desplechin film Jimmy P: Psychotherapy of a Plains Indian, starring Benicio Del Toro.
